    "Name": "Longinus",
    "Details": "The Hacked models could carry either a light machine gun or a \"David\" light gauss rifle in their right-arm modular weapon mounts, and still carried the AP weapon mount and battle claw in the left. Though effective in extending a sensor network and providing targeting data, the tradeoff in weapons, armor, and mobility was too great, and the Principality shelved the project.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Well Designed</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.908</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#2aad3b>Can only mount internal bays, can melee, can swarm.</b></color>",
