  "YangsThoughts": "The Longinus \"Hacked\" Battle armor is an experimental refit of the Longinus by Mark \"Chiphead\" Japalucci, a Tech in the Principality of Regulus, working in conjunction with Apple Computers Interstellar to help rebuild the Regulan military using salvaged technology. Taking a standard Longinus suit, reducing its jumping ability to sixty meters, shedding 120 kg of armor, and limiting the weapons payload capability, \"Chiphead\" was able to install an experimental battle armor C3i system captured from the Word of Blake.",
